{"tid":1962300,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[梁家榮點解咁夠guts]梁志祥:何君堯收視率廿萬，你頭條新聞有幾多呀?","createTime":"2020-04-07T11:28:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-07T12:50:46.000Z","uid":53000,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2fca7897682e1496443c9dda0c2285f8c7dcb5cc","tid":1962300,"uid":53000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T11:28:08.000Z","msg":"今日立法會上，民建聯梁志祥或想幫何君堯抬轎助選，指港台的節目「收視率」低，稱「何君堯收視率好高啊！廿幾萬啊隨時！」<br />\n<br />\n廣播處長梁家榮回答時，更被梁志祥急不及待地追問「處長你唔使講喇，你頭條新聞幾多(收視率)啊？」惟梁家榮糾正指梁志祥所指的其實是「點擊率」，由2019年1月到2020年2月，頭條新聞點擊率2000萬，鏗鏘集3600萬。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WNHUZRM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWNHUZRM.jpg&h=2f9f50bb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c52b1ab4b9a78ac4a22e7ab0010124fce4f5e681","tid":1962300,"uid":158457,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T11:31:00.000Z","msg":"淨係講721嗰集都百幾萬喇<br />\n廿萬都衝出嚟打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3cd2e1175d70acb1da4e59d3fdfc8cef4b4c02e","tid":1962300,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T11:31:23.000Z","msg":"跟住呢"},{"pid":"738b15189ee11fea8f396fd04e5daaa8e99cb43d","tid":1962300,"uid":189109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T11:31:29.000Z","msg":"型到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f490609b90e8680726b0cf74774c2a3b4ec8469","tid":1962300,"uid":8932,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T11:31:30.000Z","msg":"我係你就摺埋啦  梁志祥<br />\n仲衝出黎7 <br />\n你唔係以為自己好撚有料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55c4374f88605926aef11c79dd27397a52a53c05","tid":1962300,"uid":188